{"tid":1289244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布 黃碧雲係鬼！","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:38:06.000Z","uid":39180,"like":46,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27ebc585d357ed6a5dcf2eb21b33b4f5f7bc0dc7","tid":1289244,"uid":39180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"雖然一直堅持住不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n但係黃碧雲一直以來嘅一舉一動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">與鬼無誤</span></span>，仲接受閉門會議？<br />\n<br />\n反觀我地嘅戰友畫家比狗搞到咁撚樣，黃碧雲仍然帶頭妥協，所以現在正式宣布:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃碧雲係鬼！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人絕不妥協！</span></span>"},{"pid":"36b269e09055df78f18d7c6fa4c41fb4b8c969cc","tid":1289244,"uid":140326,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「兄弟爬山，各自努力」</span></span>呢句係一位政壇老前輩自己講，當時雖然佢已經分裂左第二次，但大家仍相信佢，可惜到左選舉緊張關頭，連勇武派英雄梁天琦都要屌，又話各自努力，咁你又阻兄弟爬山? fool me once, shame on you , fool me twice, shame on me, 你想fool我地第三次? 我地香港人醒覺了，終於踢走左佢。 選前話選唔到會收山，點知到而家仲頼死唔走。 連埋對上一次選舉已經露左低嘅徒弟，話自己只係借人民力量個名，無當佢地同路人。連登留意政治比較長時間嘅巴絲打， 都知道佢地係咩人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「Politics is talk」</span></span>教主講得好，基本上成個立法局無咩人好似教主咁有牙力，睇佢屌建制睇得好爽。但觀察一個人除左要聽其言，仲要觀其行，一個人口講得幾好，但言行不一致，從政多年削弱左幾多對抗政府嘅力量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「唔會同你打泥漿摔角」</span></span> 對住一班唔講理嘅人，教主知道最好對付方法就係忽略佢，教主當日咁對付痴線佬何志光。今日革命當前，分化小人當道。 好希望各位精明嘅巴絲打，可以一齊合力對付呢班分化狗，最好辦法係唔同對方理論，直接回一句<span style=\"color: red;\">「阻礙革命嘅分化狗，blocked, 上一頁」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班撚樣屌泛民仲勁過屌建制，一係on9,一係鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1288863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1288863</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44c1f1c7bfade01e823b8a3bdb35908d2642e67d","tid":1289244,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"條友不嬲都係鬼"},{"pid":"62ad12b6767000b2ce2df0b7f4db6133c543336f","tid":1289244,"uid":39085,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告民主黨切勿代表所有示威者與政府談判</span>"},{"pid":"d101f31695f68e7e212f01ecf70e82e4fdefca10","tid":1289244,"uid":177552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:20:22.000Z","msg":"呢度係熱狗集中營"},{"pid":"3d6dc01e83c8c092f4b897115b3d6bc1ac5a1de6","tid":1289244,"uid":90873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"唔係第一日既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91157055f9e76f4f11b8fadb8d74942dd0afaf85","tid":1289244,"uid":224323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:22:03.000Z","msg":"認同。 不過想講，佢從來都係。"},{"pid":"263c3e559bcc6ebc80abd29e6c9265b2126ac086","tid":1289244,"uid":28558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27ebc585d357ed6a5dcf2eb21b33b4f5f7bc0dc7","tid":1289244,"uid":39180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"雖然一直堅持住不分化，不割蓆，不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n但係黃碧雲一直以來嘅一舉一動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">與鬼無誤</span></span>，仲接受閉門會議？<br />\n<br />\n反觀我地嘅戰友畫家比狗搞到咁撚樣，黃碧雲仍然帶頭妥協，所以現在正式宣布:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃碧雲係鬼！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人絕不妥協！</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"你圍警總都主徹噃<br />\n睇黎你都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2eaa5c87c6515ba1660db4c5c3d65f487a352f3","tid":1289244,"uid":39180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263c3e559bcc6ebc80abd29e6c9265b2126ac086","tid":1289244